  "title": "Strictly Increasing Index Map",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $\\sigma:\\mathbb{N}\\to\\mathbb{N}$ be a function. The function $\\sigma$\nis a \\textbf{strictly increasing index map} if\n\\[\n k<\\ell \\Longrightarrow \\sigma(k)<\\sigma(\\ell)\n \\qquad\n \\text{for all } k,\\ell\\in\\mathbb{N}.\n\\]",
